//Biểu đồ này mô tả vòng đời của một lịch hẹn từ lúc khách hàng gửi yêu cầu cho đến khi xe được bàn giao xong.
@startuml
header AutoHub Service Management
title Detailed State Machine: Booking Lifecycle

' Cấu hình màu sắc trạng thái
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor<<Start>> #D6EAF8
    BackgroundColor<<Process>> #FCF3CF
    BackgroundColor<<Success>> #D5F5E3
    BackgroundColor<<Failed>> #FADBD8
    BorderColor #2E4053
}

[*] --> Pending : Customer submits request
note on link: Created via Web/App

state Pending <<Start>> {
    Pending : system_checks_availability()
}

Pending --> Confirmed : Admin approves slot
Pending --> Rejected : Staff rejects (busy/no parts)
Pending --> Cancelled : Customer cancels

state Confirmed <<Process>> {
    [*] --> AwaitingArrival
    AwaitingArrival --> CheckedIn : Vehicle arrives at garage
    CheckedIn --> InProgress : Technician starts work
    
    state InProgress {
        [*] --> Disassembling
        Disassembling --> Repairing
        Repairing --> Reassembling
    }
    
    InProgress --> Testing : Mechanical work done
    Testing --> InProgress : Test failed (Rework)
}

Confirmed --> Completed : Quality Assurance (QA) Passed <<Success>>
Confirmed --> Cancelled : No-show (Auto-cancel after 2h) <<Failed>>

Completed --> [*]
Rejected --> [*]
Cancelled --> [*]

legend bottom
    | Color | Description |
    | <#D6EAF8> | Initial Stage |
    | <#FCF3CF> | Active Processing |
    | <#D5F5E3> | Successful End |
    | <#FADBD8> | Terminated/Failed |
end legend
@enduml